Functional Requirements are for students the doctors and the admin / management

STUDENT functions

Register an account
Log into the system
Reset password
View available doctors
Search doctors by specialization
Check doctor availability
Book appointments
Reschedule appointments
Cancel appointments
View appointment details
View appointment history
Update profile information
View medical records
Receive appointment notifications and reminders

DOC

Log into the system
View daily appointments
View appointment details
Review patient information
Update appointment status
Add consultation notes

ADMIN

Log into the system
Manage student accounts
Manage doctor accounts
View doctor schedules
View appointment list
Generate appointment reports

Now for the Non-functional ones

The system must be user friendly and simple to use.

The system must be able to grant secure access to the system by  student, doctor, admin

The system ought to ensure that appointments are obtained fast.

The data of the user should be stored safely by the system.

The system is supposed to be available via web browsers or mobiles.
